International Olympic Committee (IOC) President Thomas Bach congratulated the China Media Group (CMG) for its contributions to the success of the broadcast coverage of the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympic Games. Replying to a letter from CMG President Shen Haixiong, President Bach said the IOC is "very appreciative of CMG's long-time commitment to the Olympic Movement and your continuous efforts in promoting the Olympic Spirit in China through the broadcast of the Olympic Winter Games Beijing 2022."